commit.message:
Fix for compile time errors when int != int_fast32_t

On most systems, int_fast32_t is int so I couldn’t find the times
where a variable is int_fast32_t in one place and int in another
place.

Fixed.

See https://github.com/samboy/MaraDNS/discussions/124
Clarify where to file a new bug report.
DwSocket: Update when root server list was last updated

Merge pull request #122 from mrfuggy/update-b-ns

Update planned renumbering for b.root-servers.net
